channel.title: I need $350, here's why. Online ways to get it?
channel.description:
Hey,
I've never wanted a material thing as bad as I want it now. I am a HUGE fan of music, and I love it. Last year for the holidays my mom gave me $300 and told me to have fun, I bought one thing, the new 30GB iPod Video. Every night before Christmas I would unwrap it ever so gently and try to sneak a peak, it was beautiful. It was the only present under the tree that was mine and I gladly would have made it the only one for the next year too. When I finally got it, I was so happy I almost knocked out. I would go [u][b]EVERY WHERE[/b][/u] with it. Sleep, shower, school(Thank Godess for long hair and hoodies), dinner table, and when it wasn't in my ears, it was on my computer charging or getting updated. Then me and my friends decided to start a buisiness selling bootleg DVD's that hadn't come out yet for $10 a piece. I made a nice chunk of change, and had only trusted people come to my house to pick up the DVDs and give me the cash. Well, out of respect I took the iPod out of my ears when they came over, and put it on the charger. The people would always come over into my room, which I had my computer in, and sit down, we'd chat for a few minutes, exchange payments, and then they would leave. After the last purchase I went outside to go to my friends to split the money (we only split after a certain amount), I forgot about my iPod because by now we were RICH. We went to the mall, spent the cash, I forgot about my iPod before we left, and I craved music the whole time we were at the mall. When I got home, I went to my room to get it, and it wasn't there. I went to got ask my mom, and figured it was in my pocket and I had forgotten it. I looked, but it wasn't there. I went and asked my mom if she took it. She said no, but that some kids came over and said that they had forgotten something in your room, so I let them in to get it. My face went white, and I asked her if it was the last person that was there with me, she said no, I was pissed. She explained what they looked like, and I had no idea who they were. I went to the person's house that we trusted, he told me no way because his mom had waited for him outside the whole time he was there and I saw the car myself so I didn't say anything, I believe him. So now, my iPod is gone. I can't call the police because I myself was doing something highly illeagle and I would bum off of my friends mp3s but it's not the same. I think it is time for my ears to have my own music flood in, off of one of my own music players. I figure if I get something, it might as well be the best. So, I am getting the $350 80GB black iPod with the free 2 line engraving on the back from, http://www.apple.com/. But I need to make the money online, because my mom won't let me use her credit card.
I've tried all of the do the free trial things, they end up costing you money in the end(why I can't use my mom's credit card anymore).
But I figure what I could do is sell RuneScape cash, and do surveys online. But I don't know any good survey sites that don't cost ME money. So, I need some cash, if anyone would be kind enough to donate even a penny, my PayPal account name is Buzzy777@gmail.com. Please post some good survey sites, I'm working on getting RS cash together now, I was always good at making RS cash.
Thanks,
Buzzy
